<font color="#FFFFFF">of the New Southern Cross.</font>

409
00:40:06,343 --> 00:40:09,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">And the only commander he serves</font>

410
00:40:09,135 --> 00:40:11,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">is the Almighty Himself.</font>

411
00:40:13,374 --> 00:40:15,374
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that your final decision?</font>

412
00:40:24,218 --> 00:40:26,175
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hmm.</font>

413
00:40:26,176 --> 00:40:29,118
<font color="#FFFFFF">My final decision is which
