417
00:40:42,352 --> 00:40:43,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's in their nature.</font>

418
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:50,677
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why don't we enlighten them?</font>

419
00:41:36,385 --> 00:41:38,259
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're right.</font>

420
00:41:38,260 --> 00:41:41,385
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have toiled in God's
service long enough.</font>

421
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:45,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">So I killed Him.</font>

422
00:41:45,613 --> 00:41:48,862
<font color="#FFFFFF">And if you want to get to Glory,
