424
00:42:26,802 --> 00:42:30,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are beautiful.</font>

425
00:42:30,135 --> 00:42:31,884
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why, thank you.</font>

426
00:42:31,885 --> 00:42:33,676
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's your name?</font>

427
00:42:33,677 --> 00:42:36,343
<font color="#FFFFFF">Emily, come here, please.</font>

428
00:43:01,093 --> 00:43:02,927
<font color="#FFFFFF">You sent out for the entertainment.</font>

429
00:43:06,425 --> 00:43:08,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, you only get to retire once, Jim.</font>

430
00:43:08,802 --> 00:43:11,259
<font color="#FFFFFF">Figured we'd do it right, hmm?</font>

431
00:43:13,135 --> 00:43:15,468
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, don't worry, they
