432
00:43:16,844 --> 00:43:20,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is a retirement party?</font>

433
00:43:20,051 --> 00:43:22,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">I couldn't tell.</font>

434
00:43:22,510 --> 00:43:24,485
<font color="#FFFFFF">Looks more like a coronation.</font>

435
00:43:26,510 --> 00:43:28,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">But no mind.</font>

436
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:30,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">Our arrangement's been a perfect fit.</font>

437
00:43:30,301 --> 00:43:32,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">You stepping down
