438
00:43:32,593 --> 00:43:33,718
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nor me.</font>

439
00:43:33,719 --> 00:43:36,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I was told I might...</font>

440
00:43:36,135 --> 00:43:37,968
<font color="#FFFFFF">I might not have to.</font>

441
00:43:37,969 --> 00:43:41,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, things are progressing, but
we'll all need a little patience.</font>

442
00:43:41,593 --> 00:43:43,788
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah, well, some of us</font>

443
00:43:43,791 --> 00:43:46,858
<font color="#FFFFFF">can afford to have more
patience than others.</font>

444
00:43:49,301 --> 00:43:50,968
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep playing, girlie.</font>

445
00:43:50,969 --> 00:43:53,452
<font color="#FFFFFF">Anything but fuckin' Chopin.</font>

446
00:44:26,311 --> 00:44:29,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you ever seen anything
so full of splendor?</font>

447
00:44:45,510 --> 00:44:47,885
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm so sorry. I didn't
mean to bother you.</font>

448
00:44:55,010 --> 00:44:56,843
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's you.</font>

449
00:44:59,677 --> 00:45:01,093
<font color="#FFFFFF">The pretty girl.</font>

450
00:45:03,510 --> 00:45:05,968
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell me your name again, pretty girl?</font>

451
00:45:07,952 --> 00:45:09,411
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm Dolores.</font>

452
00:45:11,010 --> 00:45:13,843
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dolores.</font>

453
00:45:13,844 --> 00:45:15,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Of course.</font>

454
00:45:18,413 --> 00:45:21,801
<font color="#FFFFFF">He send you down here to...</font>

455
00:45:21,802 --> 00:45:23,218
<font color="#FFFFFF">keep me company?</font>

456
00:45:24,726 --> 00:45:29,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">His sense of humor was
always somewhat... baroque.</font>

457
00:45:30,885 --> 00:45:33,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just wanted to look at the lights.</font>

458
00:45:33,510 --> 00:45:35,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">'Course you did.</font>

459
00:45:39,760 --> 00:45:42,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">So...</font>

460
00:45:42,010 --> 00:45:45,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you want to know what they're
really celebrating up there?</font>

461
00:45:45,760 --> 00:45:48,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">That, darling,</font>

462
00:45:48,593 --> 00:45:53,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">is the sound of fools fiddling...</font>

463
00:45:53,053 --> 00:45:56,762
<font color="#FFFFFF">while the whole fucking
