464
00:45:59,768 --> 00:46:03,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">And the funniest fuckin' part...</font>

465
00:46:04,855 --> 00:46:06,773
<font color="#FFFFFF">they lit the match.</font>

466
00:46:10,890 --> 00:46:13,272
<font color="#FFFFFF">So here's to you, assholes.</font>

467
00:46:17,135 --> 00:46:19,866
<font color="#FFFFFF">May your forever be blissfully short.</font>

468
00:46:43,717 --> 00:46:46,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pariah's not as welcome
as she once seemed.</font>

469
00:46:46,635 --> 00:46:49,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, the park's changin', Lawrence.</font>

470
00:46:49,143 --> 00:46:52,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is what happens when you
