471
00:47:06,677 --> 00:47:08,969
<font color="#FFFFFF">See any friends of yours?</font>

472
00:47:10,093 --> 00:47:12,007
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can't say that I do.</font>

473
00:47:19,010 --> 00:47:20,843
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm beginning to think we should have</font>

474
00:47:20,844 --> 00:47:23,843
<font color="#FFFFFF">taken our chances with the Confederados.</font>

475
00:47:23,844 --> 00:47:26,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, like you said,</font>

476
00:47:26,010 --> 00:47:29,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">we'd need an army to
