477
00:47:29,593 --> 00:47:32,718
<font color="#FFFFFF">Looks like we're about to find one.</font>

478
00:47:32,719 --> 00:47:36,175
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, whoever did this...</font>

479
00:47:36,176 --> 00:47:38,858
<font color="#FFFFFF">is someone I'm strongly
