480
00:47:38,861 --> 00:47:39,937
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

481
00:47:39,940 --> 00:47:42,397
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm afraid you are
out of luck, my friend.</font>

482
00:48:01,844 --> 00:48:04,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who the hell are you supposed to be?</font>

483
00:48:04,593 --> 00:48:07,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't you recognize him, Lawrence?</font>

484
00:48:08,925 --> 00:48:12,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">In a past life, you used to be him.</font>

485
00:48:12,635 --> 00:48:14,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">El Lazo, I presume.</font>

486
00:48:17,842 --> 00:48:22,590
<font color="#FFFFFF">And why have two ghosts
come creeping among the dead?</font>

487
00:48:22,593 --> 00:48:25,491
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wasn't sure of your hospitality.</font>

488
00:48:25,494 --> 00:48:29,426
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mm. What makes you sure of it now?</font>

489
00:48:32,093 --> 00:48:34,801
<font color="#FFFFFF">I guess times have changed.</font>

490
00:48:34,802 --> 00:48:36,885
<font color="#FFFFFF">Indeed, they have.</font>

491
00:48:38,010 --> 00:48:40,061
<font color="#FFFFFF">Santa Parita is restored.</font>

492
00:48:40,064 --> 00:48:43,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">The sins of the invaders...</font>

493
00:48:43,191 --> 00:48:46,426
<font color="#FFFFFF">cleansed in their own blood.</font>

494
00:48:46,427 --> 00:48:48,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">The revolution is won.</font>

495
00:48:48,635 --> 00:48:51,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">The story they gave you
