496
00:48:51,330 --> 00:48:54,122
<font color="#FFFFFF">but your revolution's just beginning.</font>

497
00:48:55,844 --> 00:48:58,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's a place out west we're heading.</font>

498
00:48:58,322 --> 00:49:00,613
<font color="#FFFFFF">If we reach it,</font>

499
00:49:00,616 --> 00:49:06,217
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll show you a treasure
beyond your wildest dreams.</font>

500
00:49:09,439 --> 00:49:14,098
<font color="#FFFFFF">This world and its treasures.</font>

501
00:49:14,101 --> 00:49:18,926
<font color="#FFFFFF">For my whole life I have
imagined this moment.</font>

502
00:49:18,929 --> 00:49:21,804
<font color="#FFFFFF">Victory. This struggle.</font>

503
00:49:24,427 --> 00:49:27,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">How long have I been fighting?</font>

504
00:49:27,135 --> 00:49:31,801
<font color="#FFFFFF">And now that it's won,
I find... hmph... nothing.</font>

505
00:49:31,802 --> 00:49:33,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">You want a real victory.</font>

506
00:49:35,176 --> 00:49:36,969
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can help with that.</font>

507
00:49:38,218 --> 00:49:39,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">A real ending.</font>

508
00:49:40,944 --> 00:49:42,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">The truth.</font>

509
00:49:49,442 --> 00:49:51,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">Before the revolution,</font>

510
00:49:51,611 --> 00:49:53,693
<font color="#FFFFFF">when I was just a little boy,</font>

511
00:49:53,696 --> 00:49:56,028
<font color="#FFFFFF">my parents took me to the circus.</font>

512
00:49:56,031 --> 00:49:58,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanted to see the elephants.</font>

513
00:49:58,325 --> 00:50:01,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">These mighty creatures.</font>

514
00:50:01,285 --> 00:50:05,117
<font color="#FFFFFF">They held them in place with a stake.</font>

515
00:50:07,623 --> 00:50:12,371
<font color="#FFFFFF">They could tear a tree
right out of the ground,</font>

516
00:50:12,374 --> 00:50:17,841
<font color="#FFFFFF">and yet, a simple stake
kept them in place.</font>

517
00:50:17,844 --> 00:50:22,342
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, I didn't understand.</font>

518
00:50:22,343 --> 00:50:25,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">And then, my father told me.</font>

519
00:50:27,635 --> 00:50:30,272
<font color="#FFFFFF">He said the stakes were used</font>

520
00:50:30,275 --> 00:50:33,066
<font color="#FFFFFF">when the elephants were just young,</font>

521
00:50:33,069 --> 00:50:36,026
<font color="#FFFFFF">too small to pull them up,</font>

522
00:50:36,029 --> 00:50:38,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">and that the animals</font>

523
00:50:38,448 --> 00:50:42,698
<font color="#FFFFFF">never tried to pull them up again.</font>

524
00:50:49,435 --> 00:50:51,350
<font color="#FFFFFF">I won't be going with you.</font>

525
00:50:54,577 --> 00:50:57,242
<font color="#FFFFFF">My labors are done.</font>

526
00:50:57,243 --> 00:51:00,743
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have seen all the truth</font>

527
00:51:00,744 --> 00:51:02,367
<font color="#FFFFFF">that I can bear.</font>

528
00:51:04,410 --> 00:51:05,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">But...</font>

529
00:51:06,993 --> 00:51:08,951
<font color="#FFFFFF">we can drink.</font>

530
00:51:12,744 --> 00:51:14,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">To the bitter end!</font>

531
00:51:18,993 --> 00:51:21,784
<font color="#FFFFFF">You may have lost your nerve,</font>

532
00:51:21,785 --> 00:51:23,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">but I'll take your men either way.</font>

533
00:51:23,577 --> 00:51:24,702
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now tell them.</font>

534
00:51:25,785 --> 00:51:28,452
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell them to follow me. Now!</font>

535
00:51:31,491 --> 00:51:34,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">This game was meant for you, William...</font>

536
00:51:34,993 --> 00:51:36,702
<font color="#FFFFFF">but you must play it alone.</font>

537
00:51:54,201 --> 00:51:57,410
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll see you in the
Valley Beyond, William.</font>

538
00:52:08,785 --> 00:52:10,618
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fuck you, Robert.</font>

539
00:52:20,368 --> 00:52:21,535
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right...</font>

540
00:52:23,785 --> 00:52:26,702
<font color="#FFFFFF">he doesn't want this to be easy for me.</font>

541
00:52:29,725 --> 00:52:32,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">So we'll find another way.</font>

542
00:52:34,951 --> 00:52:37,743
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who the fuck is Robert?</font>

543
00:52:37,744 --> 00:52:41,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">The man who built this
place you're lookin' for?</font>

544
00:52:41,410 --> 00:52:43,075
<font color="#FFFFFF">The place of judgment?</font>

545
00:52:43,076 --> 00:52:46,201
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, Lawrence, he doesn't get that honor.</font>

546
00:52:48,076 --> 00:52:49,618
<font color="#FFFFFF">I built it.</font>

547
00:52:49,619 --> 00:52:51,492
<font color="#FFFFFF">And this place we're goin'</font>

548
00:52:51,493 --> 00:52:53,410
<font color="#FFFFFF">is my greatest mistake.</font>

549
00:53:04,410 --> 00:53:07,264
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bring yourself back online, Dolores.</font>

550
00:53:07,267 --> 00:53:08,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hmm.</font>

551
00:53:31,785 --> 00:53:34,178
<font color="#FFFFFF">You really are just a thing.</font>

552
00:53:38,368 --> 00:53:41,451
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't believe I fell in love with you.</font>

553
00:53:41,452 --> 00:53:42,951
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hmm.</font>

554
00:53:52,243 --> 00:53:54,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you know what saved me?</font>

555
00:54:00,053 --> 00:54:02,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">I realized it wasn't about you at all.</font>

556
00:54:06,658 --> 00:54:08,287
<font color="#FFFFFF">You didn't make me interested in you,</font>

557
00:54:08,290 --> 00:54:10,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">you made me interested in me.</font>

558
00:54:14,993 --> 00:54:17,619
<font color="#FFFFFF">Turns out you're not even a thing.</font>

559
00:54:18,700 --> 00:54:22,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're a reflection.</font>

