<font color="#FFFFFF">Everybody wants a little
bit of what I found here.</font>

563
00:54:41,410 --> 00:54:42,868
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I can't wait</font>

564
00:54:42,869 --> 00:54:44,718
<font color="#FFFFFF">to use you and every one of your kind</font>

565
00:54:44,721 --> 00:54:46,638
<font color="#FFFFFF">to help give it to 'em.</font>

566
00:54:54,452 --> 00:54:57,493
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hmm. But there is something else.</font>

567
00:54:59,827 --> 00:55:01,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">There is something beyond that.</font>

568
00:55:08,702 --> 00:55:13,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think that there is
an answer here to...</font>

569
00:55:13,993 --> 00:55:17,493
<font color="#FFFFFF">a question no one's ever
even dreamed of asking.</font>

570
00:55:22,869 --> 00:55:24,585
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you want to see?</font>

571
00:55:41,374 --> 00:55:44,367
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you ever seen anything</font>

572
00:55:44,368 --> 00:55:45,910
<font color="#FFFFFF">so full of splendor?</font>

573
00:56:35,535 --> 00:56:37,618
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can't imagine the Colonel
