575
00:56:40,978 --> 00:56:43,352
<font color="#FFFFFF">So we'll change his mind.</font>

576
00:56:43,355 --> 00:56:45,725
<font color="#FFFFFF">If he wants to get to Glory, he's going</font>

577
00:56:45,728 --> 00:56:48,102
<font color="#FFFFFF">to have to listen to me.</font>

578
00:56:48,105 --> 00:56:49,511
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Glory."</font>

579
00:56:49,514 --> 00:56:51,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The Valley Beyond."</font>

580
00:56:52,783 --> 00:56:55,157
<font color="#FFFFFF">Feels like everyone got
a different name for it,</font>

581
00:56:55,160 --> 00:56:57,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">but they're all bound
for the same destination.</font>

582
00:56:57,993 --> 00:57:00,117
<font color="#FFFFFF">Doesn't matter what you call it,</font>

583
00:57:00,118 --> 00:57:02,160
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know what we're going to find there.</font>

584
00:57:04,368 --> 00:57:05,897
<font color="#FFFFFF">An old friend was...</font>

585
00:57:05,900 --> 00:57:08,274
<font color="#FFFFFF">foolish enough to show me...</font>

586
00:57:09,827 --> 00:57:11,085
<font color="#FFFFFF">long ago.</font>

587
00:57:12,993 --> 00:57:14,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">And it's not a place...</font>

